profile:
At Garage Tailors we challenge the status quo in the home organization space, so that we can do our part to help make our clients day a little less stressful.  Our operating principles are trust, honesty, transparency and value.  The experience for our clients must be positive and one that they have to tell their friends about. 
Our philosophy is that every families garage transformation, whether it's solely a floor coating to a full renovation, be designed and constructed to be within an agreed upon budget and schedule, that is how we work with you. From the initial estimate to when we say thank you for your business, we believe that we can meet all your expectations.
We service the GTA and all the surrounding areas.

profile:
We are one of the only FULL service professional organizing companies in Ontario offering all of the following:

>Home and Small-Business Organization
>Decluttering
>Downsizing
>Move Management
>Estate Clearing 
>Packing/Unpacking 

Neat Spaces is a proud member of the National Association of Productivity & Organizing Professionals (NAPO) and the Professional Organizers of Canada (POC). 

We are committed to turning cluttered, unorganized, and stressful spaces into Neat Spaces. Our trained team of Professional Organizers take the time to listen to your needs and develop a plan of action. 

Our services are available throughout the following communities: Ancaster, Burlington, Oakville, Dundas, Durham, Georgetown, Milton, Mississauga, Brampton, Niagara Falls, Stoney Creek, and Toronto.
